too much.

619
00:37:07,516 --> 00:37:08,809
He's still our dad.

620
00:37:10,728 --> 00:37:12,563
[Yubin] I think it's time for you
to forgive him.

621
00:37:12,647 --> 00:37:13,898
He's your family, after all.

622
00:37:14,857 --> 00:37:15,900
He's your father.

623
00:37:17,818 --> 00:37:20,780
Now we owe your father one.

624
00:37:24,867 --> 00:37:31,874
Forgiveness and comfort
