we're the Dongbang Group.

663
00:41:05,671 --> 00:41:08,007
Let's show them what we're made of!

664
00:41:08,090 --> 00:41:09,133
Fine, let's go!

665
00:41:09,216 --> 00:41:10,718
The Violent Crimes Team returns stronger!

666
00:41:10,801 --> 00:41:12,678
The Dongbang Group returns
